<h1>Tovali Kuami</h1>
<h3>tovalikuami371@gmail.com</h3>

<Hi, I'm Tovali Kuami, a 22-year-old IT graduate who completed my studies in 2024. I am passionate about technology, creativity, and personal growth. I enjoy building things, learning new ideas, and exploring how technology can help people and communities.

I spend my time between Eldoret and Busia, Kenya. When I’m not working with tech, I express myself through art. I love painting and singing, which allow me to share creativity and emotion in different ways.

I also enjoy watching games from time to time and spending moments reflecting on life and improving myself. I believe in self-confidence, creativity, and using my skills to grow and inspire others.

This website is a place where I share my thoughts, creativity, and experiences as I continue my journey in technology and art..</p>

